{"tid":539522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以後講粗口就要停學","createTime":"2018-01-24T15:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T15:46:07.000Z","uid":50457,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"604277be2138c06bbcb8583bc83de42e4fc4f25b","tid":539522,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T15:24:27.000Z","msg":"咁廢老講粗口就要停止發放津貼<br />\n<br />\n地盤佬，巴士佬，廚房佬講粗口都要炒<br />\n<br />\nCCTVB出現劇集有粗口就要取消牌照<br />\n<br />\n舉中指睇怕都要切手指吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n基本上而家大學生就係原罪，被社會權貴瘋狂打壓<br />\n<br />\n咁講殺無赦呢？要唔要勾利筋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網打粗口應該都要封帳號<br />\n<br />\n成班雞蛋，幫高牆一齊打壓雞蛋，呢個香港絕對可以用光怪陸離去描述"},{"pid":"2a23328812f61eb9ae486a0d367a88835cfa2d1c","tid":539522,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T15:39:55.000Z","msg":"仲有，踢波，街市買菜，一般隨街聽人講電話，都充斥住大量粗口，咒罵。<br />\n<br />\n唔通又要遣責，又解僱？<br />\n<br />\n仲衰過中共的廣檢局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n乜香港人突然全部變晒文人？睇完新聞班人的反應未一樣粗口爛舌<br />\n<br />\n而家擺到明係有權力的一群借頭借路，大力打壓。而且掌控傳媒，睇到班雞蛋幫高牆開聲，真係好笑"},{"pid":"d9c832f9f0dd1a4d369af2ff4019169b41a369cf","tid":539522,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T15:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f413b5b29185153b57706167d9e7f3dc30db8093","tid":539522,"uid":63670,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T15:46:07.000Z","msg":"睇人仆街最開心<br />\n<br />\n有得落井下石更加係爽丫丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有咩開心得過可以踩班平時無機會踩既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}